---
import cinemaAnimation from "../assets/cinema.webp";
import puntingAnimation from "../assets/punting.webp";
import pubAnimation from "../assets/pub.webp";
---

<script>
    const goToRsvpButton = document.querySelector("#go-to-rsvp");
    const rsvpElement = document.querySelector("#introduction");

    if (goToRsvpButton !== null && rsvpElement !== null) {
        goToRsvpButton.addEventListener("click", () => {
            rsvpElement.scrollIntoView({
                behavior: "smooth",
            });
        });
    }
</script>

<section>
    <article>
        <p id="introduction">
            Hello! We would love for you to join us in celebration of a few
            things; our birthdays, spending 10 years together, our engagement
            and most importantly: all of you! We are so grateful for all the
            connections we have made and look forward to celebrating these
            landmarks amongst loved ones.
        </p>
        <a href="https://forms.gle/xMqRGD7k1xMCmoq77" target="_blank">
            <p id="rsvp" class="padded-section">RSVP</p>
        </a>

        <h2 id="date" class="padded-section">Saturday 1st August 2026</h2>
        <div class="event">
            <img
                class="event-animation"
                src={cinemaAnimation.src}
                alt=""
                fetchpriority="high"
            />
            <p class="event-title">
                <a href="https://uppcinema.com/" target="_blank">Cinema</a>
            </p>
            <div class="event-details">
                <div>
                    <p class="time">14:00 - 17:00</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>Ultimate Picture Palace</p>
                    <p>Jeune St Cowley Rd</p>
                    <p>Oxford OX4 1BN</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="event">
            <img
                class="event-animation"
                src={puntingAnimation.src}
                alt=""
                fetchpriority="high"
            />
            <p class="event-title">
                <a href="https://www.oxfordpunting.co.uk/" target="_blank">
                    Punting
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="event-details">
                <div>
                    <p class="time">17:00 - 18:30</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>Magdalen Bridge Boathouse</p>
                    <p>High Street</p>
                    <p>Oxford OX1 4AU</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="event">
            <img
                class="event-animation"
                src={pubAnimation.src}
                alt=""
                fetchpriority="high"
            />
            <p class="event-title">
                <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/starpuboxford/?hl=en"
                    target="_blank">Pub</a
                >
            </p>
            <div class="event-details">
                <div>
                    <p class="time">18:30 - Late</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p>The Star</p>
                    <p>21 Rectory Rd</p>
                    <p>Oxford OX4 1BU</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h3 id="travelandaccom" class="narrow-body padded-section">
            Travel and Accommodation
        </h3>
        <div id="travelandaccom-body" class="narrow-body">
            <p class="travel-train">Train</p>
            <div>
                <p>
                    Oxford Railway Station is an easy destination for most! From
                    London, you can travel from either Paddington or Marylebone.
                </p>
                <p>
                    From the train station, it is a 35 minute walk to the
                    Ultimate Picture Palace. Alternatively, there are a number
                    of buses (1, 3, 5, 400, 3A ) you can take from the station
                    that will take 14-18 minutes with minimal walking!
                </p>
                <p class="travel-car">Car</p>
                <div>
                    <p>
                        Depending on parking options with your accommodation, we
                        suggest using one of the Park and Ride sites around
                        Oxford. There is free bus travel from these sites!
                        Please check the <a
                            href="https://www.oxford.gov.uk/parkandridesites"
                            target="_blank">Oxford City Council website</a
                        > to find out which site is best suited for you. The maximum
                        stay is 72 hours.
                    </p>
                    <p class="accommodation">Accommodation</p>
                    <div>
                        <p>
                            For those who want the true Oxford experience, it's
                            worth checking out <a
                                href="https://www.universityrooms.com/en-GB/city/oxford/home/"
                                target="_blank">University Rooms</a
                            > which offers unoccupied rooms in college rooms which
                            are maintained as a Bed and Breakfast! Central options
                            if you want to explore more of the city.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Most affordable options include <a
                                href="https://hotels.cloudbeds.com/en/reservation/k1RHbB/?currency=gbp"
                                target="_blank">Central Backpackers Hostel</a
                            > and budget hotels such as <a
                                href="https://www.premierinn.com/gb/en/hotels/england/oxfordshire/oxford/oxford-cowley.html"
                                target="_blank">Premier Inn</a
                            > and <a
                                href="https://www.easyhotel.com/hotels/united-kingdom/oxford/oxford?utm_source=google&utm_medium=cpc&utm_campaign=BA__EASYHOTEL_OXFORD__NAME__EN_UK_BA_4252_402&campaign_type=SEARCH&utm_term=easyhotel%20oxford&device=c&gad_source=1&gad_campaignid=13692642138&gbraid=0AAAAAD-lD5TqmCFiIQLdT3NDR7RYa0kQu&gclid=CjwKCAjwxb7RBhA5EiwAQ-AAdFBc99jnSP9TotKNwIUvTha09C_As__Kj4pw__-YZo0Bz-rqmxMoGRoCPBcQAvD_BwE"
                                target="_blank">easyHotel</a
                            >.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            If you want to hit the hay without too much travel, <a
                                href="https://themadhatteroxford.com/house-of-hatter-3/"
                                target="_blank">The Mad Hatter</a
                            > and <a
                                href="https://www.no192oxford.co.uk/en/"
                                target="_blank">No. 192</a
                            > are very close to all locations on 1st August at a mid-tier
                            price.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Fancy treating yourself? <a
                                href="https://thestoreoxford.com/"
                                target="_blank">The Store</a
                            > is a beautiful and central hotel for those looking for
                            a more luxurious option, only a 20-25 minute walk to Cowley.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4 id="generalquestions" class="padded-section">General Questions</h4>
        <div id="general-answers" class="narrow-body">
            <p class="dresscode">Dress Code</p>
            <p>
                This is a semi-formal event, but please dress however will make
                you feel confident and comfortable!
            </p>
            <p>
                We politely request that guests avoid wearing white and red as
                these are traditional bridal colours in our respective cultures.
            </p>
            <p>
                For those who would appreciate further guidance, please reach
                out.
            </p>
            <p class="venueinformation">Venue Information</p>
            <p>
                The day will be both an outdoor and indoor event, so please
                dress appropriately for weather conditions. In the unfortunate
                circumstance of rain, there will be an indoor area of the pub.
            </p>
            <p>
                We will have dinner and drinks at the pub in the evening, so
                it's advisable to eat before arriving at the cinema. Please
                mention your dietary and accessibility requirements when you
                RSVP.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="go-to-rsvp-container">
            <div id="go-to-rsvp">Time to RSVP ↑</div>
        </div>

        <style>
            article {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                font-family: var(--font-nanum-myeongjo);
                padding-top: 150px;
                padding-right: 30px;
                padding-left: 30px;
                padding-bottom: 100px;
            }

            @media only screen and (min-width: 768px) {
                padding-right: 150px;
                padding-left: 150px;
            }

            #introduction {
                font-size: 18px;
                max-width: 1000px;
            }

            @media only screen and (min-width: 740px) {
                #introduction {
                    font-size: 25px;
                }
            }

            .padded-section {
                padding-top: 50px;
            }

            @media only screen and (min-width: 740px) {
                .padded-section {
                    padding-top: 200px;
                }
            }

            #rsvp {
                color: #80c0ff;
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 40px;
                text-decoration-line: underline;
                text-decoration-style: dotted;
                text-underline-offset: 5px;©
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 50px;
            }

            #date {
                text-align: center;
            }

            .event {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .event-animation {
                width: 70%;
            }

            .event-title {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 30px;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-top: 0px;
            }

            .event-details {
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 40px;
                font-size: 18px;
                display: grid;
                grid-auto-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
                grid-auto-flow: column;
            }

            @media only screen and (min-width: 740px) {
                .event-details {
                    gap: 100px;
                    font-size: 20px;
                }
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 50px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .time {
                white-space: nowrap;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .narrow-body {
                max-width: 600px;
            }

            #travelandaccom-body {
                text-align: justify;
            }

            .travel-train {
                font-size: 25px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .travel-car {
                padding-top: 20px;
                font-size: 25px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .accommodation {
                padding-top: 20px;
                font-size: 25px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            @media only screen and (min-width: 740px) {
                .travel-train {
                    padding-top: 30px;
                }

                .travel-car {
                    padding-top: 50px;
                }
                .accommodation {
                    padding-top: 50px;
                }
            }

            a:link {
                color: grey;
                background-color: transparent;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            a:visited {
                color: grey;
                background-color: transparent;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            a:hover {
                color: #80c0ff;
                background-color: transparent;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            h4 {
                font-size: 50px;
                text-align: center;
                max-width: 600px;
            }

            .dresscode {
                padding-top: 30px;
                font-size: 25px;
                font-weight: bold;
                max-width: 600px;
            }

            .venueinformation {
                padding-top: 50px;
                font-size: 25px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            #general-answers {
                text-align: justify;
            }

            #go-to-rsvp-container {
                padding-top: 50px;
            }

            #go-to-rsvp {
                color: gray;
                text-align: center;
                cursor: pointer;
                user-select: none;
            }

            #go-to-rsvp:hover {
                color: #80c0ff;
                background-color: transparent;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
        </style>
    </article>
</section>
